  <sect1>
    <title>
      Introduction
    </title>
    <p>
      In this chapter we explore some of the parts of the CLDR that you might only find useful for
      very specific applications. We recommend that you skim through this chapter, just to
      be aware of what's possible, so that you can revisit it later if the need arises.

      Some of the topics include the formatting of lists, person names, URL route localization
      (for SEO purposes), etc.
    </p>
  </sect1>

