  <sect1>
    <title>
      In summary
    </title>
    <p>
      In this chapter we dived into some of the murkier depths of the CLDR.
      Mileage may vary, but if you happen to have an application that has a need for something like
      gender-aware translations, rules-based number formatting or localized calendar UIs,
      then this chapter will have equipped you with a programattic approach for
      tackling these challenges. In the right scenario, this can be staggeringly useful,
      so please sit back, relax, and think of all the countless if-statements you've just
      saved yourself from having to maintain.
    </p>
